in windows, build
- download visual studio
- in a terminal with cl (vcvarsall.bat), run build.bat

in linux, build
- install openssl lib
- run build.sh

how to use?
- update your host file to include 127.0.0.1 l2authd.lineage2.com
- run login_server
- that's it, open your lineage 2 client and enjoy. accounts are created automatically

notes
- the login server uses the port 2106
- the game server will automatically use the port 7777 

credits
- l2j: https://www.l2jserver.com
- openssl: https://www.openssl.org
- blowfish: https://github.com/Rupan/blowfish/tree/master
